#: ../../I/Itanic.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Intel Itanium, so called in reference to the legendary disaster that was"
" the Titanic. This term bubbled up in several places on the Internet in 1999"
" when it was beginning to become clear that the Itanium was turning into the"
" most expensive and protracted flop in the history of the semiconductor "
"industry."
msgstr ""
"Intel "
"Itaniumのこと。タイタニック号の伝説的な大惨事になぞらえてこう呼ばれる。この用語は1999年に、Itaniumが半導体産業の歴史上最も高価で長期にわたる失敗作になりつつあることが明らかになり始めたとき、インターネットの複数の場所で湧き上がった。"
